reviews.text: Let me tell you right now . Cocos is my lifeline. It gets me through my week just knowing I can order this delicious pizza on a Saturday and devour it with my precious family. 100 stars .
A great local business with flavor. We love your hoagies and pizza, and one stop shopping for beer and snacks. Always a friendly smile and fast service. You supply our community with great taste!

I've been coming to the Aston Cocco's for a while now, and I won't go anywhere else. The staff are fantastic, friendly, and helpful. The atmosphere at Cocco's is great. It's relaxing and I can enjoy dinner with my friends/husband etc, and it's not loud. The food (pizza, cheese steaks, French fries) is very good and it's cooked perfectly. 20/10 I'll come here every time.

Pizza has always been good here. Service just ok. Fries were slightly burnt but I know its not a regular thing.
Good for kids parties
Welcoming, friendly, fast service with great wait staff. Chicken Caesar wrap is great! beer list is eclectic too! Definitely will be back for lunch sometime soon!
